trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of change occurring in a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Angir typen endring inntreffer i en samling av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerActionListsChangedType enumeration indicates that an element has been added or removed from a managed collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen DesignerActionListsChangedType indikerer at et element har lagt til eller fjernes fra en forvaltet samling <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekter.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class, which is associated with the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Denne nummerering brukes i den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>klassen som er knyttet til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>hendelsen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Although the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects, it does not directly raise events.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Selv om den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>klassen er en samling av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekter, den ikke heve hendelser direkte.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Én eller flere <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekter har blitt lagt til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Én eller flere <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekter har blitt fjernet fra samlingen.
